y-submit\" type=\"button\">Add</button>\r\n<strong>Maritime Name System (MNS) Dummy</strong> saves MRN-locator mapping information entries. It appears under the managing panel.\r\nModel <strong>1</strong> is polling client model. Model <strong>2</strong> is service provider (server) model.\r\nModel <strong>1</strong> need not have correct IP and port number. (e.g. IP=1.1.1.1 and port number=0)\r\nModel <strong>2</strong> must have correct IP and port number that MMS server can access.\r\nBe careful that model <strong>2</strong> may not receive messages due to its firewalls, NAT or line sharer(공유기), etc.\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Remove MNS entry having MRN=</a><input id=\"remove-mrn\" type=\"text\" />  <button id=\"remove-mns-entry-submit\" type=\"button\">Remove</button></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Add the MRN you are debugging. MRN=</a><input id=\"add-mrn-being-debugged\" type=\"text\" />  <button id=\"add-mrn-being-debugged-submit\" type=\"button\">Add</button>\r\nRegister the MRN in <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>.\r\nBegin collecting logs related to the MRN being debugged.\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Remove the MRN you are not debugging anymore. MRN=</a><input id=\"remove-mrn-being-debugged\" type=\"text\" />  <button id=\"remove-mrn-being-debugged-submit\" type=\"button\">Remove</button>\r\nRemove the MRN from <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>.\r\nStop collecting logs related to the MRN being debugged. Then remove the logs.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Add the ID consuming realtime log service. ID=</a><input id=\"add-id-realtime-log-ids\" type=\"text\" />  <button id=\"add-id-realtime-log-ids-submit\" type=\"button\">Add</button>\r\nRegister the ID in <strong>Realtime log service consumer IDs</strong>.\r\nBegin collecting realtime logs for the ID.\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Remove the ID not consuming realtime log service anymore. ID=</a><input id=\"remove-id-realtime-log-ids\" type=\"text\" />  <button id=\"remove-id-realtime-log-ids-submit\" type=\"button\">Remove</button>\r\nRemove the ID from <strong>Realtime log service consumer IDs</strong>.\r\nStop collecting logs for the ID. Then remove the logs.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<button id=\"hide-managing-panel\" style=\"background-color: #6699ff;\" type=\"button\">Hide Managing Panel</button>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The MRN you are debugging now. MRN=</a><input id=\"mrn-being-debugged\" type=\"text\" />  <button id=\"mrn-being-debugged-submit\" type=\"button\">view logs</button>  <button id=\"return-to-status-page\" type=\"button\">return</button>\r\nOnly the logs related to the MRN being debugged are shown.\r\nFirst, the MRN must be registered in <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>.\r\nIn order to regiser a MRN in <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>, use the function in <strong>the managing panel</strong>.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"padding-left: 14.4px;\">MMS\'s Maritime Resource Name: <strong>urn:mrn:smart-navi:device:mms1</strong>. Addresses: <strong>http://192.168.0.104:8088</strong>, <strong>https://192.168.0.104:444</strong>.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[includeme src=\"http://192.168.0.104:8088/status\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"1200\" id=\"mms-status\"]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div id=\"invisible-container\" style=\"display: none;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"display:none;\"> <pre> //Please cut and paste this code into below Scripts and Styles.\r\njQuery(document).ready(function() {\r\n	var mms_url = \'http://192.168.0.104:8088\'; \r\n	var mms_url_extern = \'http://192.168.0.104:8088\';  \r\n	\r\n	if (location.protocol == \'https:\')\r\n	{\r\n		mms_url = \'https://192.168.0.104:444\';\r\n		mms_url_extern = \'https://192.168.0.104:444\';\r\n	}\r\n	\r\n	jQuery(\"#show-managing-panel\").click(function() {\r\n		